---
title: Honey-Soy Chicken & Toasted Sesame Sauce with Kumara Fries & Pear Salad
description: Who doesn’t love the classic combo of honey and soy? We teamed this signature mix with succulent chicken, baked kumara fries and a refreshing Asian-style pear salad for a meal that you won’t be able to resist!
